title: The Cosy Club
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, British, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. UK chain restaurant serving a variety of different food including British classics, tapas, burgers, sandwiches, and brunch. This one was built in an old hospital with high ceilings, wooden floors, and quirky interiors. Kitchen stops at 10pm.
streetAddress: Halford Wing, Dean Clarke House, 1 Southernhay Gardens
